Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:40.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is a businessman's town. I snuck in somehow by graduating from a state college.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:45.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I get my ass kicked by my superiors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:51.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you yearn to be like that just to get by in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:54.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The city of winter, where I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:02:00.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But all that seems far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:03.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All that's in front of me is the azure of the South China Sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:04.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The clamoring wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:05.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:12.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right Mr. Japanese, I'm going to ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:17.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The one package you got from Asahi Industries in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:22.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The one you're in charge of until you hand it over to the chief in Borneo. This is it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:23.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:25.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But what I want to ask is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:27.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:29.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's everything we were going to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:31.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch, this is a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:33.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot him in his knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:34.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He'll start singing like a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:35.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:39.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That one disk is more than enough for the payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:41.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Payment, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:41.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:42.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:44.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you through yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:47.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone heading straight for us from Supick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably a scout from the Filipino Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:54.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic Benny-Boy, everything's taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:56.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Start the engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:02:59.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,OK, gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:04.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to disperse and then you'll be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:09.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But the deal's off if anyone decides to come after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:12.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What you see there is a torpedo launcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:17.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to be blown out of the water, then stay still for the next half hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:19.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then you will be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:22.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:24.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting relaxed over?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:26.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:27.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dipshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:28.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:29.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're joking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:32.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're joking, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Japan is getting further away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:46.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Black Lagoon to Balalaika.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:46.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:49.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:50.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How is the target?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:51.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:54.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Smart jobs are lovely, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:56.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The trade-off goes as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:57.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, just as promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:04.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Connect me to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:08.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How about an explanation,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Investigational Department Chief Kageyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:13.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,About the case we have been informed about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:16.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let me explain the situation to you further.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:21.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Today at 4pm the Burgenbiria Trade Company contacted us...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:27.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...regarding the negotiations for the disk stolen from the Meramarsia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:29.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Russian Mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:41.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The front for the group that aims to take top position after displacing the Chinese Mafia from Southeast Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:44.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are they after specifically? Money?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:48.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely the route to Southeast Asia where the barter is going to take place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:55.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They wish to take part in some of our more unsavory trade routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Blackmail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:59.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's shameful, having something to be blackmailed about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:05.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But they do not seem to know what's really on the disk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:11.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If they find out it will be the worst scandal since the founding of Asahi Industries.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:12.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:19.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A report from Jakarta has just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:25.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,According to a local Chinese merchant, the Russian Mafia has yet to receive the disk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:31.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The disk is still in the hands of the pirates that attacked the Meramarsia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:33.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is our chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:37.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We can't trust the word of the Mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:41.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We must take the disk before it reaches them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:45.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Before it reaches them? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:52.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. The board will leave this matter in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:55.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Choosing what actions to take will also be your responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:06:01.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, what do you plan on doing with the hostage? Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:05.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:06.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:09.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This job is twenty grand! Only twenty grand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:12.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's so wrong about collecting a bonus with a ransom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:15.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're being simple-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:16.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You want to be killed, Benny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:17.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:21.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who's going to negotiate with Japan? You?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:23.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have their phone number?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:26.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How about a bank account to accept the ransom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:27.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:30.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just kill his ass and throw him in the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:31.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:34.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Don't damage the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:35.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:42.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch. Dutch, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, so let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:46.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,OK, Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play it cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:49.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:52.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive. I don't know why, but I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:56.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right. Let's go topside for a smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:02.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:07.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll contact your company somehow and set up a trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:12.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A ransom, huh? This'll go on my permanent record.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:14.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But we have our own priorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:18.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Getting the disk to the client comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:20.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So there's a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:23.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're just delivery boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:27.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We brush up against the law from time to time, so we can eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:28.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But that's business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:33.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is what they call the Stockholm Syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:40.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment, I feel like this big guy next to me is the only one I can trust in this whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:43.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:45.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:47.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okajima Rokuro
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the name of that employee?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:53.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's Okajima, Director. Okajima Rokuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:57.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is entirely the fault of my managerial skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:08:00.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:04.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was only informed recently, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:07.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And because there were no other employees we could trust with vital information,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:11.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,there was some time lost in communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:12.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have an opinion, Kageyama-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:18.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Our company is in a crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:21.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot accept any more delays.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:28.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The E.O. Company, with whom we've made a secret contract, have already sent their mercenaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:33.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was your responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:37.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I feel bad for this employee. What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:42.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's Okajima, Director. Okajima Rokuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:50.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:53.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:54.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think he means you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:58.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:01.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere to get a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:05.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought I was a hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I'm coming too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:13.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But where on Earth is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:39.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:42.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why is there a pistol on every table?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:46.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a Western movie bar, at the end of the World?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not a bad analogy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:53.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This place was started by the losers of the Vietnam War.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:58.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They started taking in deserters too and before we knew it, it went to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:02.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hookers, junkies, mercs, killers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:04.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Irredeemable criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you dislike it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:08.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese pubs...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:12.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I love those unguarded smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:14.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Places like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:17.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up or I'll throw you out onto the beach. Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:20.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not suited for fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:23.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have that kind of face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Benny, I'm going to make a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's a weird guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:35.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,After being around him for two years all I know is that he's tough, intelligent and weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:37.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Give up on trying to understand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:38.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:41.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You seem different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:43.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:45.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A college in Florida.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:49.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Playing with fire pissed off the Mafia and the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:50.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:55.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I saved his ass before he was used as a weight in a suitcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:57.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this worthless storytelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:00.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're not old enough to be reminiscing about the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One for you, one for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We came all the way here for a drink,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:11.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,let's talk about something a littler cooler, Mr. Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:12.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:22.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Beer's as good as piss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:24.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you drink, you don't get drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:25.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a man you'll drink rum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:29.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But if... you're a wuss who can't even take a challenge from a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:31.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I won't force you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:37.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll make you wear a skirt, put on ribbons and take you to a dance party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:41.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I hate chugging down drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:43.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:57.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're forced to drink at company socials. Don't mock a Japanese businessman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:11:59.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:03.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, bartender.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bring all the Bacardi you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:11.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, I thought you didn't like fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:14.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:16.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:20.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't trust Asahi Industries' response.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:26.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So I left out bait, and a Chinese rat bit. I'm talking to it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:28.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who's on the move?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:29.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:32.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Say you're owner's name loudly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:36.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shinginan's Wan Taikei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:40.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wan Taikei sent an assassin to get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:42.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He sent an assassin to Roanapur!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:43.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:45.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:50.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me the number and affiliation of those soldiers. Hurry, we're busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:55.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Guys from Extra Order, a mercenary contracting agency! I don't know how many there are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:59.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The E.O. Company scouts experienced war junkies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:00.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just our luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:01.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For god's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:24.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,OK, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:25.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's party time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:38.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Give any runners extra assholes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:41.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure there are only corpses when we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:53.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, if they are your friends then you deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:55.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:58.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've bulletproofed the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It can handle up to a .50 caliber.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:01.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:03.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Benny!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miraculously, I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:06.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How about Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:07.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:08.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,People are dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:11.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I finally graduated a state college and got into a good company!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:12.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:14.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry, dipshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:16.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to enjoy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:18.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Or you'll end up wasting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:25.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy! Show them why you're named Two-Hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:29.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:31.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I heard a voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:35.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I hate survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:38.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He says good things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:58.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Got 'em, Dutch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:00.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:01.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:03.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How many times have you destroyed my shop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You owe me for all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:11.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Or I'll weld your asshole shut and make you a new one on your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:12.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:13.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:23.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:24.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:28.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:31.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think, at this rate, trading you is out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:33.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:35.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we didn't make any plans to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:37.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What if we just part ways here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:39.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:41.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to die! Take me with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:42.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:44.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't pull our leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:46.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, we're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:47.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:15:59.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:07.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, you war junkies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:15.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch, Bao was so pissed he looked like a steaming pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:18.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we pay him back he's going to weld our assholes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:22.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Scary. Makes me want to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:24.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:25.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:27.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:30.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is a lot more entertaining than Hollywood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:35.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, 16 dead, 8 wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:39.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry sir. We thought they were punks and underestimated them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:43.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shutorm, they're not punks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:46.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're somebodies we can go after.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:50.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All we had to shoot at were old men and brats in Liberia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow and no fight left in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:57.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But these guys are full of fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:00.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:06.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If we stay at this speed we'll be at the Balawan Port by daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:08.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet Balalaika there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:10.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So... Rock,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:15.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Benny is getting in touch with your company.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can pull it off if you try, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:25.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If negotiations don't go well, we're going to have to leave you around Malaya. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:31.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There are bandits all around, but you shouldn't die immediately. OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:34.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What? You bring me this far and you're going to let me die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:38.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?! After dragging me all over the place,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,at least take me somewhere safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:47.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,First you cry then you want to use us like a taxi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:49.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:53.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can show you what color your brain is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:53.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:55.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:58.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're using an Assault Dial so it's secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:01.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, it's your boss, Kageyama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:06.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Department Chief! It's Okajima, I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:09.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,About the disk...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:11.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:15.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That disk no longer exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:17.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:21.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the situation, I'll tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:23.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:32.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to explain, but we were hired to help develop nuclear capabilities for a certain country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:35.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The disk contained the plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:39.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:41.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nukes in this day and age.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And war...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:45.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually I will be at the top and do something about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:49.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but this can't be made public.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:54.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okajima-kun, for the sake of the 50,000 employees of Asahi Industries, disappear into the South China Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:59.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be promoted to chief and we won't treat you badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:04.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And the president and everyone under him will be at your funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:09.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The professional ruffians should almost be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:11.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's my equipment status?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fully equipped, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:16.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rockets and machine guns, the more you shoot the more the invoice will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:18.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Japanese are very generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:19.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:33.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You were ditched pretty easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:35.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I sympathize, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:39.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And the ransom bonus is all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:42.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But is that enough to make you sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:43.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:44.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:44.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you on the deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:45.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:50.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's something coming straight at us over the ocean, but it's not a boat, it's too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:53.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At 3 hours 5 minutes. Can you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:01.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A low-altitude assault gunship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:04.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,God damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:05.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,An assault helicopter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:06.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:11.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to see them, I can smell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:14.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn them. Using that to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:16.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock! Hold this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:20.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A gun?! Don't make me hold this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:23.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be more than a comfort, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:25.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming. He's on our ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:28.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not good, not good. This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:30.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's shooting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:36.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know, it's not good, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:37.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:39.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:40.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:42.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You try it, dipshit Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:45.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're hiding under a torpedo launcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:48.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get blown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:52.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:54.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:55.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:57.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You impotent son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:58.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna run away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:02.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I need to suffer like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:09.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, we're just gonna watch from up high.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:13.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But Captain, we can turn them into mincemeat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:16.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:19.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,From their heads to their tails, they're in my trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:24.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to laugh at them while they cry, howl and piss themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:26.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:30.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You do and say whatever you want to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.06,0:21:33.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, even the Department Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:40.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I need to suffer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.12,0:23:20.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:21.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You told me that.
